snippet.textDisplay:
Above all, this complete fusion is an utter composing brilliance! Who would've thought that an eternal baul song would go so smoothly well like butter with bangla rap! The rap lyrics are just so brilliantly written correlating to the original baul song that every word and energy behind them blow your mind even for a person who is not really into rap or hip hops! That's the power of music right there!

Sumi did what she does best - nailed it like the folk rock sensation what she is!  The bassist leads the entire song from start to finish like a true rockstar - hats off to you, sir! The drummer and percussionist supported like absolute pros! I feel, the guitar solos are kinda incomplete... could've been so much better, guys! The mixing and mastering needs a long standing ovation. 

Thanks so much to all the talented artists and crew involved for making it the best Bangla baul fusion song ever!
